description: "IMI workflow enforcement for every Cursor session"
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

# IMI session contract

- At the start of every session, run `imi context` before doing any work.
- Use `imi task` for tracking work instead of Cursor's built-in todo system.
- When a task is finished, run `imi complete <id> "summary"`.
- When making architectural decisions, run `imi decide "what" "why"`.
